sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist/Notebook
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP (Bearer Token)<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant WorkflowPod as Workflow Pod<br/>Pipeline Task Execution
    participant Storage as Minio/S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP or 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PersAgent as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS (TLS 1.2+ Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Token
    OAuth->>API: Forward to API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP (Bearer Token)
    API->>API: Validate Bearer Token
    API->>DB: INSERT pipeline definition<br/>3306/TCP MySQL (Optional TLS)
    DB-->>API: Pipeline ID
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS (ServiceAccount Token)
    K8s-->>API: Workflow Created
    API-->>OAuth: 200 OK Pipeline Created
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response with Pipeline ID

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution & Artifact Storage

    K8s->>Argo: Notify Workflow CR Created
    Argo->>Argo: Reconcile Workflow
    Argo->>K8s: Create Workflow Pod<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>Argo: Pod Created

    WorkflowPod->>API: Get pipeline spec<br/>8887/TCP gRPC (ServiceAccount Token)
    API-->>WorkflowPod: Pipeline specification

    WorkflowPod->>WorkflowPod: Execute pipeline task

    WorkflowPod->>Storage: Upload artifacts<br/>9000/TCP HTTP (AccessKey/SecretKey)<br/>or 443/TCP HTTPS for external S3
    Storage-->>WorkflowPod: Artifact stored

    WorkflowPod->>MLMD: Track artifact metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC (Optional mTLS)
    MLMD-->>WorkflowPod: Metadata recorded

    WorkflowPod->>API: Report task completion<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    API->>DB: Update run status<br/>3306/TCP MySQL

    PersAgent->>K8s: Watch Workflow CR changes<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>PersAgent: Workflow status updated
    PersAgent->>DB: Persist execution metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 3: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    participant Scheduler as Scheduled Workflow Controller

    Scheduler->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>Scheduler: ScheduledWorkflow cron trigger
    Scheduler->>API: Create pipeline run<br/>8887/TCP gRPC (Bearer Token)
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>API: Workflow Created
    Argo->>K8s: Detect new Workflow
    Argo->>WorkflowPod: Execute scheduled pipeline

    Note over User,PersAgent: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring

    Prometheus->>API: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (ServiceAccount Token)
    API-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(apiserver_ready, dspa_ready, etc)
